to lure out the suspect.

00:32:17.010 --> 00:32:19.796
F*ck, I was right beside you!

00:32:21.680 --> 00:32:22.680
So what?

00:32:23.060 --> 00:32:24.356
Sooner or later,

00:32:24.400 --> 00:32:25.880
I still figure out what you’re up to.

00:32:26.330 --> 00:32:28.189
Even if you killed everyone here,

00:32:28.218 --> 00:32:29.541
do you think you can get away?

00:32:29.563 --> 00:32:30.778
Who would ever believe you?

00:32:32.500 --> 00:32:33.985
Then you can be the first to die.

00:32:35.160 --> 00:32:36.160
Tan!

00:32:40.100 --> 00:32:41.105
That’s not it!

00:32:41.800 --> 00:32:43.316
Petchkla never cheated

00:32:43.880 --> 00:32:45.694
